OL,3,CRoofer jailed for leaving widow almost
OL,4,C#13,000 out of pocket
OL,6,FThese included that his child and wife
OL,7,Fwere seriously ill and he that had
OL,8,Fbeen diagnosed with cancer, that he
OL,9,Fwas repeatedly let down by
OL,10,Fscaffolders, that the weather was too
OL,11,Fbad to work on the roof, and that he
OL,12,Fhad crashed his van.
OL,14,FOnly an ineffective membrane protected
OL,15,Fthe property from the weather
OL,16,Fthroughout the winter months, and
OL,17,Ffinally at this point, the victim
OL,18,Frealised that Parr was never going to
OL,19,Freturn.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
