OL,3,CRoofer jailed for leaving widow almost
OL,4,C#13,000 out of pocket
OL,6,FThe report also stated that it was
OL,7,Fhighly unlikely, based on the rest of
OL,8,Fthe roof, that the roof Parr had
OL,9,Fremoved needed replacing, as he had
OL,10,Fclaimed.
OL,12,FThough Trading Standards offered him a
OL,13,Fseries of opportunities to speak to
OL,14,Fthem and give them his side of the
OL,15,Fstory, he repeatedly failed to show up
OL,16,Fand eventually he was summoned to
OL,17,Fcourt, but didn't turn up for the
OL,18,Ffirst hearing there either.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
