OL,3,CRoofer jailed for leaving widow almost
OL,4,C#13,000 out of pocket
OL,6,FHe was also ordered to pay his
OL,7,FLancashire victim #1,300 compensation
OL,8,Fand received a prison sentence for
OL,9,Fthis case and benefit fraud cases,
OL,10,Fbringing his total time inside to 39
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FCouncillor Barbara Bentham, lead
OL,14,Fmember for neighbourhoods, environment
OL,15,Fand community safety said: "I'm
OL,16,Fpleased to hear this sentence today
OL,17,Fand I hope it sends a strong message
OL,18,Fto rogue traders who prey on
OL,19,Fvulnerable people in our city.
